    • addCrewMember

      public boolean addCrewMember(CrewMember member)
      This method adds a crew member to the cabin, ensuring that: - If the cabin is empty, two humans will be added. - If an alien is provided, only one alien can be added. - The cabin cannot accommodate mixed types (i.e., humans and aliens cannot coexist in the same cabin).
      Parameters:
      member - The crew member to be added. This can be either a Human or an Alien.
      Returns:
      true if the crew member was successfully added to the cabin; false if the cabin is already full or if the attempt to mix crew types fails.
